OL,3,CScottish postman admits brutally
OL,4,Cmurdering girlfriend
OL,6,FA man has admitted murdering and
OL,7,Fdecapitating his 21-year-old
OL,8,Fgirlfriend before texting her mother
OL,9,Fpretending to be her.
OL,11,FEwan Methven, now 27, murdered Phoenix
OL,12,FSpencer-Horn, 21, in the home they
OL,13,Fshared on November 16 last year, after
OL,14,Fthe couple ordered a takeaway to their
OL,15,Fflat in Glen Lee, East Kilbride, on a
OL,16,FSaturday night.
