OL,3,CScottish postman admits brutally
OL,4,Cmurdering girlfriend
OL,6,FEarlier that day, Methven, who worked
OL,7,Fas a postman for Royal Mail, had
OL,8,Fcomplained to his girlfriend that her
OL,9,Fwaitress shifts made him "lonely", and
OL,10,Fshe had exchanged messages with her
OL,11,Fmother, Alison Spencer, at around
OL,12,F9.37pm, saying they were eating dinner.
OL,14,FThe couple had been together for two
OL,15,Fyears and met at a family party, the
OL,16,FHigh Court in Glasgow was told.
