OL,3,CScottish postman admits brutally
OL,4,Cmurdering girlfriend
OL,6,FAt around midnight on the Saturday,
OL,7,FMethven attacked Miss Spencer-Horn
OL,8,Fwith three knives, stabbing her 20
OL,9,Ftimes, before mutilating her body and
OL,10,Fsevering her head with three knives,
OL,11,Fthe court heard.
OL,13,FHe spent the weekend driving Miss
OL,14,FSpencer-Horn's red Corsa, scrolling
OL,15,Fthrough her phone and searching for
OL,16,Finternet pornography, as well as
OL,17,Fmaking several attempts to buy
OL,18,Fcocaine, the court heard.
