OL,3,CScottish postman admits brutally
OL,4,Cmurdering girlfriend
OL,6,FThe court heard a food order was
OL,7,Fplaced around 8pm and Methven "did not
OL,8,Fappear to be drunk or under the
OL,9,Finfluence by the delivery driver",
OL,10,Fhowever in a 999 call he claimed the
OL,11,Fmurder happened when he had a
OL,12,Fpsychotic episode induced by cocaine,
OL,13,Falcohol and steroids.
OL,15,FOn Tuesday, Methven pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fmurder and attempting to defeat the
OL,17,Fends of justice at the High Court in
OL,18,FGlasgow.
