OL,6,FProsecutor Christopher McKenna told
OL,7,Fthe court at around 2.40am, Methven
OL,8,Fmessaged a drug dealer to seek drugs,
OL,9,Fand sent similar messages the
OL,10,Ffollowing day and in the early hours
OL,11,Fof November 18.
OL,13,FHe also exchanged messages with Ms
OL,14,FSpencer-Horn's mother, claiming the
OL,15,Fcouple had been "drunk" and that her
OL,16,Fdaughter was asleep, the court heard.
OL,18,FMethven said in one text: "Hey, Phe
OL,19,Fisn't up yet, I'll get her to text you
OL,20,Fwhen she is x."
