OL,6,FMethven admitted attempting to remove
OL,7,Fthe limbs and torso from her body with
OL,8,Fa knife or other instrument.
OL,10,FPathologists believe Ms Spencer-Horn
OL,11,Fmay have been attacked in the bathroom
OL,12,Fbefore being dragged into the hall,
OL,13,Fbut a bloodied knife was also found in
OL,14,Fthe bedroom, the court heard.
OL,16,FDefending, Tony Graham KC said Methven
OL,17,Fhad wanted to plead guilty to "provide
OL,18,Fclosure".
